               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 2ra-130rb)
 -
                     Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 2ra-7rb)
 - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat
                     ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 15ra-22vb)
 - Homily
                     by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 75va-77va)
 - Homily by St
                     Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 106vb-114vb)
                     - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols. 126ra-129rb)
 - Mangada
                     samāy “Journey to Heaven” (fols. 129rb-130rb)
 II) Ṣalota śǝryätä ḫaṭiʾat
                     “Prayer of Absolution of Sins” (fols. 121vb-126ra), (cf. EMML no.
                     127(9)).</summary>
