               <provenance>ʾIyasu is mentioned in the supplication
                     formulas on 10va, 28vb, 95rb, 96vb; his name is
                     inserted interlineally on several fols., e.g., 89rb, 91va, 92rab. The name
                     Ḫiruta Śǝllāse is added interlineally in a secondary hand on 10va, 28vb, 45va, 91va, 115vb; Nǝṣḥa Dǝngǝl is
                     mentioned on several fols., e.g., 28vb, 72ra, 81rb, 95rb, 96va; Walda ʾIyasu is
                     mentioned on several fols., e.g., 92vb, 93ra, 94vb; the names of several other
                     people are also mentioned.</provenance></history>
